OL,3,CJersey deputy fined for speeding and
OL,4,Cfailing to display a valid insurance
OL,5,Cdisc
OL,7,FA Jersey politician has been fined
OL,8,Falmost #600 for speeding and failing
OL,9,Fto display a valid insurance disc in
OL,10,Fhis car.
OL,12,FDeputy Philip Ozouf appeared at
OL,13,FJersey's Magistrate's Court this
OL,14,Fmorning (Tuesday 11 February).
OL,16,FHe pleaded guilty to both offences and
OL,17,Fwas handed a total fine of #575.
