OL,3,CJersey deputy fined for speeding and
OL,4,Cfailing to display a valid insurance
OL,5,Cdisc
OL,7,FMr Ozouf was stopped by a police
OL,8,Fofficer on Saturday 2 November 2024.
OL,9,FHe was driving a silver BMW at 31mph
OL,10,Fin an area with a speed limit of
OL,11,F15mph. There were no other passengers
OL,12,Fin the vehicle.
OL,14,FThe insurance disk on display had an
OL,15,Fexpiry date of June 2023.
OL,17,FMr Ozouf then failed to provide proof
OL,18,Fof insurance within the seven days
OL,19,Fthat followed however documentation
OL,20,Fwas provided a day later which showed
OL,21,Fhe was appropriately covered.
