OL,3,CJersey deputy fined for speeding and
OL,4,Cfailing to display a valid insurance
OL,5,Cdisc
OL,7,FFor the charge of speeding the judge
OL,8,Ffined Mr Ozouf #275 and endorsed his
OL,9,Fdriving licence.
OL,11,FRegarding the failure to display and
OL,12,Fprovide proof of insurance, the judge
OL,13,Fagreed this was an "oversight" but
OL,14,Ffined him #300.
OL,16,FThe court heard that the Deputy for St
OL,17,FSaviour had been invited to an enquiry
OL,18,Fat his local Parish Hall on three
OL,19,Foccasions but failed to attend.
